  :comment: Hello! If the skits don't appear, may be you might increase the temperature
    (may be 155C may be 160). I bake in gas oven, and 140C is enough for macaron,
    sometimes they wanted to burst and then I opoen the oven for some seconds. I wisk
    only one part of whites, another whites just mix with almond and sugar powders.
